SONG OF ICE - v0.1

Song of Ice is a passive game, meant to provide a relaxing but interactive musical experience. The levels require very little skill to complete, but should provide the user some musical and visual entertainment value.

LICENSE
-------------
Not yet determined.

Content license - Some of the content included in Song of Ice cannot be included in other works.

PREREQUISITES
-------------
In order to build Song of Ice, you must have the Microsoft XNA Game Studio Version 3.1, and some version of Microsoft Visual C# (The Express Edition is free and does the job).

BUILDING
-------------
Open: Ice/Ice.sln in Visual C#.
Build the project.

PLAYING
--------------
The game rules are not yet determined. Further instructions on how to play will be added here when the game rules are finalized.